		<IRequirement type="e">
			<_id type="a">GUID f30f0b90-8c11-4c37-8421-161a588d66ad</_id>
			<_myState type="a">8192</_myState>
			<_name type="a">Stopping</_name>
			<_modifiedTimeWeak type="a">1.2.1990::0:0:0</_modifiedTimeWeak>
			<_description type="p"><IDescription type="e">
				<_text type="a">Stopping%0D
Stopping the gate may result from reaching one of the end positions or the occurrence of a collision.%0D
The procedure should in order:%0D
1. Switch off the drive%0D
2. Turn off the collision detector%0D
3. Optionally, turn off the signal lamp</_text>
			</IDescription>
			</_description>
			<_modifiedTime type="a">6.2.2026::10:33:45</_modifiedTime>
			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1250\deff0\deflang1045{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset238{\*\fname Arial;}Arial CE;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 Stopping\par%0D
Stopping the gate may result from reaching one of the end positions or the occurrence of a collision.\par%0D
The procedure should in order:\par%0D
1. Switch off the drive\par%0D
2. Turn off the collision detector\par%0D
3. Optionally, turn off the signal lamp\par%0D
}%0D
</_body>
		</IRequirement>
		<IRequirement type="e">
			<_id type="a">GUID 65819928-f1ac-4340-9e2d-c914b0f15d53</_id>
			<_myState type="a">8192</_myState>
			<_name type="a">Testing</_name>
			<_modifiedTimeWeak type="a">1.2.1990::0:0:0</_modifiedTimeWeak>
			<_description type="p"><IDescription type="e">
				<_text type="a">Testing%0D
Testing invovles sending the 'is_ok()' message to the modules and reading the returned value. If the value is not returned within the specified time, the test is considered failed</_text>
			</IDescription>
			</_description>
			<_modifiedTime type="a">6.2.2026::10:35:7</_modifiedTime>
			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1250\deff0\deflang1045{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset238{\*\fname Arial;}Arial CE;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 Testing\par%0D
Testing invovles sending the 'is_ok()' message to the modules and reading the returned value. If the value is not returned within the specified time, the test is considered failed\par%0D
\par%0D
}%0D
</_body>
		</IRequirement>
